DE_VERBUS_BETA
                                      BY SPYDR
                                 VERSION : BETA1
                                ABOUT THE MAP

it is a small but (hopefully) Competitive map with gameplay in mind.
unlike most maps, it has 2 hard jumps that goes to the same location.
although it gives a VERY OP View from middle.
                                  DEV NOTES
the map is still in beta, and NOTHING is complete.
the layout still needs some fixing and such.
feel free to post any suggestions!
                                       FILES
The Download File has LOTS of stuffs.
it has files you can toy with. (even has the original compile log, unedited!)

INCLUDES :

BSP FILE
ORIGINAL COMPILE LOG
VMF FILE (for editing in hammer)
VMX FILE (don's know what this is for, probably some sort of backup when you loose the original vmf file.)
PRT FILE (Again, don't know what this is for.)

Thank You For viewing (and maybe even downloading) this map!
May God Bless you!
